**Tests:**
- Unit (capture_run_test.go, mirroring capture_test.go helpers initCaptureRepo/execute/
  readRunManifest): happy path 3-stage spec -> ONE run with 3 stages, correct
  skills/models/inputs/output, artifacts readable from the ref; run-level defaults applied
