- Error cases: missing spec file; malformed YAML; unknown field (KnownFields); missing
  run_id; stage missing skill.id; stage with zero/two outputs; nonexistent artifact path;
  duplicate stage names / Manifest.Validate failure surfaced; run ref already exists
  (create-only collision).
- Built-binary manual test (CLI bead, ref-mutating -> THROWAWAY temp repo per
  capture-protocol Internal Loops rule): `go build -o $tmp/etude ./cmd/etude`; in a
  `mktemp -d` + `git init` + seed one commit: write a sample 2-3 stage run spec + artifact
  files, run `$tmp/etude capture-run spec.yaml`, confirm exactly ONE `refs/etude/runs/<id>`
  ref exists with all stages + artifacts, and `$tmp/etude run show <id>` renders every
  stage/skill/model. Never run against the working repo.

