- Low. Reuses shipped WriteManifestTree + artifactstore + yaml.v3; the only new surface is a
  spec parser. Main care point: artifact-path resolution (relative to spec dir) must be
  unambiguous and tested. Create-only semantics keep it from clobbering existing runs.

